00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.854
Rainbow Mille Crepes, Crepe Cake

00:00:18.510 --> 00:00:19.390
Crepe Batter

00:00:19.390 --> 00:00:23.110
First, add all the ingredients for crepes in a blend. The ingredients are in the description box below.

00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:56.480
And blend until smooth.

00:01:07.229 --> 00:01:08.269
Rainbow Batter

00:01:11.060 --> 00:01:13.940
Divide the batter equally in 6 containers. 

00:01:19.440 --> 00:01:24.596
And mix with food colors to make red, orange, yellow, green, blue, and violet.

00:01:42.360 --> 00:01:44.360
Make Crepes.

00:01:47.060 --> 00:01:50.140
Brush a frying pan with butter. 

00:01:50.300 --> 00:01:52.360
And over medium heat cook 2 or 3 tablespoons of the batter at a time. 

00:01:52.640 --> 00:01:55.620
Spread the batter thinly and evenly. 

00:01:56.780 --> 00:02:00.040
When the top is dry, flip it over and cook for another 20 seconds. 

00:02:01.120 --> 00:02:03.475
Repeat until the batter is finished.

00:02:23.480 --> 00:02:25.000
Whipped Cream Filling

00:02:25.175 --> 00:02:28.855
Whisk the whipping cream, adding in sugar and vanilla.

00:02:35.398 --> 00:02:36.518
Make The Rainbow

00:02:36.980 --> 00:02:39.076
Start with violet layer and finish with red.

00:02:41.980 --> 00:02:44.940
Fill with whipped cream between the layers.

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:29.560
Chill in the refrigerator for at least 2 hours.

00:03:41.480 --> 00:03:45.320
And serve with jam, syrup, ice cream, whipped cream, etc.

